<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <p>For each transaction, will fail the test if the profit/loss generated from the transaction, calculated on a per unit impact basis is greater than the tolerance set.</p>
        <p>This validation is intended to check each transaction record to ensure that the P&amp;L of the transaction does not represent more than a specified percentage on a per unit basis.</p>
        <p>This is a validation that calculates a difference between two values on a per unit basis and tests that % difference against the tolerances set for the validation.</p>
        <p>Will check purchase and sale transactions only.</p>
    </body>
</html>